what you wanted to hear.

1316
01:27:49,912 --> 01:27:52,538
With full humility
and utmost gratitude...

1317
01:27:52,749 --> 01:27:54,874
...I accept this great honor...

1318
01:27:55,085 --> 01:27:59,128
...and I promise I will do my
best to represent my nation...

1319
01:27:59,295 --> 01:28:02,800
...my planet and my
God on this historic...

1320
01:28:02,965 --> 01:28:04,049
...journey.

