01:42:35,177 --> 01:42:36,893
Digital microchip good for

1541
01:42:36,894 --> 01:42:39,140
thousands of
hours of recording.

1542
01:42:40,433 --> 01:42:42,600
Okay, look, I understand...

1543
01:42:42,851 --> 01:42:46,186
