01:43:49,828 --> 01:43:52,957
There are 1,000 reasons we
can think of to have this...

1566
01:43:53,166 --> 01:43:56,085
...but mostly it's for the
reasons we can't think of.

1567
01:44:22,608 --> 01:44:23,776
Come in.

1568
01:44:25,277 --> 01:44:27,613
Dr. Arroway, time to get ready.

1569
01:44:27,862 --> 01:44:28,864
Thank you.

1570
01:44:39,957 --> 01:44:41,710
I know there's not much time.

1571
01:44:41,874 --> 01:44:44,921
As soon as I found out about
it, I called the President.

1572
01:44:45,129 --> 01:44:46,797
I came with Kitz.

