not the real one.

1579
01:45:02,896 --> 01:45:04,897
I didn't vote for you to go...

1580
01:45:06,775 --> 01:45:08,610
...because I don't
want to lose you.

1581
01:45:09,737 --> 01:45:11,903
Now you find your
way home, all right?

1582
01:45:28,877 --> 01:45:30,295
23 hours ago, the world...

1583
01:45:30,545 --> 01:45:32,480
...was stunned by
the announcement

1584
01:45:32,481 --> 01:45:34,633
of the existence of
another Machine...

1585
01:45:34,842 --> 01:45:37,802
...and its passenger,
Eleanor Ann Arroway.

1586
01:45:38,011 --> 01:45:38,594
Now...

1587
01:45:39,219 --> 01:45:41,640
...the question that's
on everyone's mind:

1588
01:45:41,848 --> 01:45:43,598
Will history repeat itself?

1589
01:45:44,016 --> 01:45:46,352
With a piece of
engineering this complex...

1590
01:45:46,518 --> 01:45:50,564
...with so many unknowns,
could the unthinkable occur?

1591
01:45:50,772 --> 01:45:54,108
The security in Hokkaido
has been incredibly tight.

1592
01:45:54,275 --> 01:45:57,654
No reporters whatsoever have
been allowed near the site.

1593
01:48:38,174 --> 01:48:41,177
Restraint secure. Life
support functions normal.

1594
01:48:41,386 --> 01:48:42,262
Roger.

1595
01:48:42,470 --> 01:48:44,471
This is Control. Do you copy?

1596
01:48:44,682 --> 01:48:46,182
Reading you
five-by-five.

1597
01:48:47,224 --> 01:48:48,642
Give me Ellie's PRD.

1598
01:48:48,892 --> 01:48:50,894
Video unit recording
