1599
01:48:52,272 --> 01:48:54,856
- Are you reading me?
- That's affirmative.

1600
01:48:55,065 --> 01:48:56,733
Video looks good.

1601
01:48:57,568 --> 01:48:58,693
Copy, Control.

1602
01:49:00,111 --> 01:49:02,905
Ellie, we're going to
proceed to button you up.

1603
01:49:04,782 --> 01:49:05,949
I'm ready.

