- Can we boost signal?
- It's at maximum.

1654
01:52:22,838 --> 01:52:24,131
65%.

1655
01:52:24,340 --> 01:52:26,007
The material is changing.

1656
01:52:26,216 --> 01:52:29,676
It's bordering on translucence.
The system's intact.

1657
01:52:33,013 --> 01:52:34,556
It has to be...

1658
01:52:34,766 --> 01:52:37,309
...some kind of
electromagnetic field.

1659
01:52:37,558 --> 01:52:38,603
Do you read this?

1660
01:52:38,853 --> 01:52:40,855
We see only interference.

1661
01:52:40,897 --> 01:52:42,396
It's becoming translucent.

1662
01:52:43,272 --> 01:52:45,775
I can't describe it. I
can't even explain it!

1663
01:52:48,569 --> 01:52:49,528
70%.

1664
01:52:49,736 --> 01:52:52,073
We have intermittent
comm, but we are go!

