01:52:52,407 --> 01:52:54,408
Initiate secondary
drive systems.

1666
01:52:54,616 --> 01:52:56,702
Initiating auxiliary
booster sequence.

1667
01:52:56,910 --> 01:52:58,453
We're go for ignition.

1668
01:53:05,794 --> 01:53:07,378
We have auxiliary ignition.

1669
01:53:13,926 --> 01:53:15,428
Life support, how is she?

1670
01:53:15,595 --> 01:53:18,472
Heart and respiration are
