1676
01:53:41,826 --> 01:53:43,995
Control, if you're
reading me...

1677
01:53:44,287 --> 01:53:46,498
...I am okay to go! Okay to go!

1678
01:53:46,832 --> 01:53:47,791
85%.

1679
01:53:47,957 --> 01:53:49,375
