01:54:27,410 --> 01:54:28,912
100% target velocity.

1688
01:54:30,454 --> 01:54:32,743
Tremendous EMI
levels around Machine!

1689
01:54:32,744 --> 01:54:34,791
Field measurements
are off-scale.

1690
01:54:35,000 --> 01:54:37,337
We're approaching
our abort limits.

1691
01:54:39,838 --> 01:54:40,964
Okay to go.

1692
01:54:46,136 --> 01:54:46,970
I hear her!

1693
01:54:47,512 --> 01:54:50,429
I hear her. Barely,
but she's there.

1694
01:54:50,681 --> 01:54:51,847
Okay to go.

1695
01:54:52,226 --> 01:54:53,601
Says she's okay to go.

1696
01:54:56,646 --> 01:54:58,480
Steve, we're real close.

1697
01:54:58,812 --> 01:54:59,848
- Your core reading?

1698
01:54:59,849 --> 01:55:01,816
- Internal environment
looks normal.

1699
01:55:02,192 --> 01:55:04,903
Inside the core, the
weather's beautiful.

1700
01:55:08,990 --> 01:55:10,282
I'm okay to go.

1701
01:55:12,785 --> 01:55:14,245
I'm okay to go.

1702
