On my mark.

1704
01:55:22,084 --> 01:55:23,085
10...

1705
01:55:23,628 --> 01:55:24,671
...9...

1706
01:55:25,672 --> 01:55:26,672
...8...

1707
01:55:28,214 --> 01:55:29,217
...7...

